-- Rhodia Aims to Double 2015 Asia Sales to $2.8 Billion, Les Echos Reports
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-25T04:57:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/rhodia-aims-to-double-2015-asia-sales-to-2-8-billion-les-echos-reports.html
Rhodia SA aims to double its sales
in Asia to 2 billion euros in 2015, French daily Les Echos
reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Jean-Pierre Clamadieu.  The company plans to make two acquisitions in India next
year, each for a few dozen million dollars, the newspaper added,
without citing anyone.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  